	   <tr><td colspan=2>Arguments on who's better or who should drop dead is just absurd, we all got into this game without knowing which is the most "kick ass".  We follow our style to pick a class, so there's just no reason to attack other classes.  Let's not forget if one class doesn't perform well in the end game it's Verant that didn't balance the classes well.  Let's stop flaming on each other's abilities nor declaring you own all other classes.  <br>Monks in my opinion is great. Although I am a paladin am gifted w/ little down time and better tanking ability, but I admire the FD ability and recognize such ability is equally as useful as warrior's slash and hack.  I respect all classes coz a Norrath filled w/ only warrior/enchanter/clerics would be just boring.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
